name: Reimbursement for services of advanced practice registered nurses
text: §432:1-611  Reimbursement for services of advanced practice registered nurses.  All individual and group hospital and medical service plan contracts and medical service corporation contracts under this article shall provide reimbursement for health plan-covered services provided by advanced practice registered nurses licensed pursuant to chapter 457. [L 1999, c 222, §1; am L 2015, c 35, §48]
